Update: 1.24.26 2 new images added, 3 replaced for uncensored versions by nyoronyan (pages 78 79 and 80)

Welcome to the ultimate vanellope mega lolicon collection!
This gallery is sourced from pixiv, baraag, paheal, twitter/X, e-hentai, and many more sites around the internet from many different artists!

All the highest quality sources i could find. Not AI-generated AI-upscaled or altered in anyway, other than the occasional uncensoring i may find and mostly uncensored content by default. this gallery is mostly NSFW but there is some SFW art in here too.

Most everything is pretty well organized at this point, but you may still see some things get moved around every now and then or dubs deleted etc.

I removed a few images by a certain artist. The reason for this is i know they removed a bunch of their art from here and i dont want my entire gallery nuked just cause a few of their paywall images got included in the mix.
But that doesnt mean i still wont include them here. ;)
